VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bLinking\.openURL\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:allowlist|Linking\.canOpenURL|validateUrl|startsWith.*https|trustedDomains && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects external URL launches that require strict allowlist validation.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Arbitrary External URL Opening.
